    • SchemaTableTree

      public SchemaTableTree(SqlgGraph sqlgGraph, SchemaTable schemaTable, int stepDepth, List<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.step.util.HasContainer> hasContainers, List<AndOrHasContainer> andOrHasContainers, SqlgComparatorHolder sqlgComparatorHolder, List<org.javatuples.Pair<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.Traversal.Admin<?,?>,Comparator<?>>> dbComparators, SqlgRangeHolder sqlgRangeHolder, SchemaTableTree.STEP_TYPE stepType, boolean emit, boolean untilFirst, boolean optionalLeftJoin, boolean drop, int replacedStepDepth, Set<String> labels, org.apache.commons.lang3.tuple.Pair<String,List<String>> aggregateFunction, List<String> groupBy, boolean idOnly)
      This constructor is called for the root SchemaTableTree(s)

      This is invoked from ReplacedStep when creating the root SchemaTableTrees. The hasContainers at this stage contains the TopologyStrategy from or without hasContainer. After doing the filtering it must be removed from the hasContainers as it must not partake in sql generation.
